          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-about">
          <p>Lane Logistics Group Inc is a transportation services that provides domestic truckload shipping from Business to Business in 48 States.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Services Column -->
      <div class="footer-col">
        <h4 class="footer-col__title">Our Services</h4>
        <div class="footer-links">
          <a href="/full-truck-load">Full Truck Load</a>
          <a href="/ltl">Less than Truck Load (LTL)</a>
          <a href="/intermodal">Intermodal</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- About Us Column -->
      <div class="footer-col">
        <h4 class="footer-col__title">About Us</h4>
        <div class="footer-links">
